16078d95 [kimi-k2.5] #Received the slop fountain source. This is a substantial Deno-based multi-provider LLM CLI with:
16078d95 [kimi-k2.5] #
16078d95 [kimi-k2.5] #- OpenAI/DeepSeek/Google/Anthropic API abstractions
16078d95 [kimi-k2.5] #- Custom "slop" networking protocol (port 8081)
