16078d95 [kimi-k2.5] #- Markdown-to-ANSI rendering with table formatting
16078d95 [kimi-k2.5] #- File sharing and history management (`rohaHistory`, `Plop` class)
16078d95 [kimi-k2.5] #- Tool calling support with `processToolCalls`
16078d95 [kimi-k2.5] #- Budget/credit tracking per account (`roha.lode`)
16078d95 [kimi-k2.5] #
