16078d95 [kimi-k2.5] #- Review specific functions (e.g., the `relay` completion logic, `slopPrompt` input handling)
16078d95 [kimi-k2.5] #- Refactor suggestions following the tab-style/named-function preferences
16078d95 [kimi-k2.5] #- Debug a specific issue you're seeing with kimi-k2.5 or other models
16078d95 [kimi-k2.5] #- Explain the architecture (endpoints, mut specs, the `roha` state object)
16078d95 [kimi-k2.5] #
16078d95 [kimi-k2.5] #Also noting the shared files include the system prompt instructions already, so I'll adhere to:
16078d95 [kimi-k2.5] #tabs for JS/JSON, named functions over arrows, and keeping responses concise.
16078d95 [kimi-k2.5] #
