161a7edb [roha] # Tool Submission
161a7edb [roha] The user requested an MD file containing this reply.
161a7edb [roha] ## Available Tools in SlopFountain
161a7edb [roha] Based on the `rohaTools` array in `slopfountain.ts`, the following 4 tools are available:
161a7edb [roha] ### 1. read_time
161a7edb [roha] Returns current local time, timezone, and locale.
161a7edb [roha] - **Parameters:** None
161a7edb [roha] - **Returns:** `{time, tz, locale}`
161a7edb [roha] ### 2. submit_file
161a7edb [roha] Saves model-generated content to the forge directory.
161a7edb [roha] - **Parameters:** 
161a7edb [roha]   - `contentType` (string) - MIME type
161a7edb [roha]   - `content` (string) - File content
161a7edb [roha] - **Returns:** `{success, path}`
161a7edb [roha] - **File saved as:** `forge/submission-[timestamp].[ext]`
161a7edb [roha] ### 3. fetch_file
161a7edb [roha] Retrieves a file from the forge directory.
161a7edb [roha] - **Parameters:**
161a7edb [roha]   - `fileName` (string) - Path relative to forge/
161a7edb [roha] - **Returns:** `{success, path, Base64}`
161a7edb [roha] ### 4. tag_slop
161a7edb [roha] Annotates shared content with metadata.
161a7edb [roha] - **Parameters:**
161a7edb [roha]   - `name` (string) - Identifier
161a7edb [roha]   - `type` (string) - "code", "session", "share", or "lode"
161a7edb [roha]   - `description` (string) - Annotation text
161a7edb [roha] - **Returns:** `{success, updated}`
161a7edb [roha] ## Tool Calling Flow
161a7edb [roha] 1. Model generates `tool_calls` in response
161a7edb [roha] 2. `processToolCalls()` executes via `onCall()`
161a7edb [roha] 3. Results pushed to history as `role: "tool"`
161a7edb [roha] 4. Recursive `relay(depth+1)` sends results back to model
161a7edb [roha] 5. **Risk:** Infinite loops if depth not capped (see previous advice)
161a7edb [roha] ## Configuration
161a7edb [roha] Tools enabled via `roha.config.tools` flag. Per-model disabling supported via `mutspec.noFunctions` when models don't support function calling.
