162906ae [kimi-k2.5] #
162906ae [kimi-k2.5] #• slopfountain.ts* - Main application (~125KB)
162906ae [kimi-k2.5] #- Multi-provider support: OpenAI, DeepSeek, Google (Gemini), Anthropic (Claude)
162906ae [kimi-k2.5] #- Persistent state via "forge" JSON (configs, history, shares, budgets)
