162906ae [kimi-k2.5] #- Cost tracking per model/account with credit management
162906ae [kimi-k2.5] #- ANSI markdown rendering with Discord-compatible table formatting
162906ae [kimi-k2.5] #- Voice synthesis support (Gemini TTS, OpenAI, macOS `say`)
162906ae [kimi-k2.5] #
162906ae [kimi-k2.5] #• slopprompt.ts* - Raw terminal input handler (~19KB)
