162906ae [kimi-k2.5] #- History navigation (arrow keys)
162906ae [kimi-k2.5] #- Shortcode expansion (`:heart:` → ❤️)
162906ae [kimi-k2.5] #- TCP listener (port 8081) for remote/SSH sessions
162906ae [kimi-k2.5] #- NDJSON message protocol for real-time broadcasting
162906ae [kimi-k2.5] #
162906ae [kimi-k2.5] #Key Features
162906ae [kimi-k2.5] #
162906ae [kimi-k2.5] #- Model abstraction: Unified interface across providers with "mut" naming (strips version
162906ae [kimi-k2.5] #cruft like `-preview`, `-distill`)
162906ae [kimi-k2.5] #- File sharing: Hash-based deduplication, size limits, MIME type detection
162906ae [kimi-k2.5] #- History modes: Plain, strict, multi-modal (vision), inline (Gemini-style)
162906ae [kimi-k2.5] #- Budget tracking: Per-account credit management with pricing tables
