167253ba [kimi-k2.5] #• Slop Fountain Architecture Acknowledged*
167253ba [kimi-k2.5] #
167253ba [kimi-k2.5] #Multi-transport LLM gateway with Deno. Key observations:
167253ba [kimi-k2.5] #
167253ba [kimi-k2.5] #• Protocol*
167253ba [kimi-k2.5] #- Raw TCP/NDJSON on 8081 for inter-process slop relay
167253ba [kimi-k2.5] #- Unix sockets (`/tmp/sloppy.sock`) and SSH (6669) for alternative ingress
167253ba [kimi-k2.5] #- Discord bot egress via GatewayIntentBits
167253ba [kimi-k2.5] #
167253ba [kimi-k2.5] #• Temperature Modes*
167253ba [kimi-k2.5] #- Frigid (🧊): `cold: true` models (o4-mini, kimi-k2.5, gpt-5-nano) - temperature locked
167253ba [kimi-k2.5] #- Variable: 0.7 default via `grokTemperature`, -5 to 50 range
167253ba [kimi-k2.5] #
167253ba [kimi-k2.5] #• Frontends*
167253ba [kimi-k2.5] #- Raw mode: Custom grapheme-clustered prompt with `slopprompt.ts` (Intl.Segmenter, CSI handling)
167253ba [kimi-k2.5] #- HTTP: Deno.serve with JSON-RPC (sys.info, sys.tick, sys.ports)
167253ba [kimi-k2.5] #- Workers: `slophole.ts` singleton pattern for off-main-thread TCP
167253ba [kimi-k2.5] #
167253ba [kimi-k2.5] #• Unicode Handling*
167253ba [kimi-k2.5] #- Dual width calculation: `stringWidth()` (terminal) vs `discordStringWidth()` (2.5/1.5 wide chars)
167253ba [kimi-k2.5] #- `slopspec.json` hieroglyph ranges (1313F-133CF) and box-drawing (2500-256C)
167253ba [kimi-k2.5] #
167253ba [kimi-k2.5] #• Cost Tracking*
167253ba [kimi-k2.5] #- Per-account credit decrement in `roha.lode[account].credit`
167253ba [kimi-k2.5] #- Pricing tiers from modelspecs (input/cache/output rates)
167253ba [kimi-k2.5] #
167253ba [kimi-k2.5] #Ready for `/push` and model relay testing.
167253ba [kimi-k2.5] #
